com.diffplug.common.rx

Interface IObservable<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ObservableSource<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RxBox<T>, RxGetter<T>, RxLockBox<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Breaker, ForwardingBox.Rx, ForwardingBox.RxLock

    public interface IObservable<T>
extends ObservableSource<T>
    An object which can be supplied in an Observable form. Ideally, `io.reactivex.Observable` would be an interface, which would make this interface unnecessary. But so long as it isn't, this (combined with Rx) makes it fairly seamless to fix this.
